text: Mariano Antonelli (born 24 June 1933) is an Italian former sports shooter. He competed in the 50 metre rifle, prone event at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1933 births Category:Living people Category:People from the Province of L'Aquila Category:Italian male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Italy Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics
